    "description": "Celebi India International Enterprises is actively seeking a talented and motivated Reservation Manager to join our dynamic team in Patna. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Celebi India International Enterprises:\nCelebi India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Celebi India International Enterprises!",
